Check out our weekly @NoisiaRadio podcast.

Noisia comprise Dutch producers Thijs, Nik and Martijn. Largely regarded as one of the most distinctive, powerful acts to emerge in bass music, their production techniques are referenced and praised across the entire electronic music scene. Their extensive body of work also includes the game Devil May Cry and the Foreign Beggars collaboration I Am Legion.

iTunes: http://itun.es/i6J824m Beatport: http://btprt.dj/10bptJI

Bonus Version (36 tracks, 81 minutes): 
iTunes: http://itun.es/i6J32sJ
Beatport: http://btprt.dj/VI74zV
Amazon: http://amzn.to/XgUIgU
Spotify: http://spoti.fi/10c9FX0

Download a free sample from the soundtrack: http://on.fb.me/LglBvv

The soundtrack CD is available EXCLUSIVELY through our webshop at http://www.noisia.nl Anyone who buys the CD will also receive the bonus version digitally!

This is a game soundtrack, not a new Noisia album. Its full of ambiences and unexpected pieces of music. Don't expect to buy 18 or 36 dancefloor bangers :)

Like Noisia on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/noisia
Follow Noisia on Twitter: http://twitter.com/#!/Noisia_nl
Listen to Noisia on Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/noisia

Devil May Cry is out January 15th 2013: http://on.fb.me/WqFW4H
